title: Not So Jolly Rodgers
description:
Mina is joined by Justis Mosqueda of SB Nation to break down the Green Bay Packers and the rest of the NFC. Plus, Mike Ryan Ruiz stops by to talk about what’s going on with the Cleveland Browns and his AFC power rankings.
